metadata.name: Gemini in Pluto
metadata.description:
Those who know that things are transformed from the invisible can see the real, that which the others call madness, too many metaphors, too much literalness and midpoints… take the entropy by the throat and recreate everything without asking.
Regardless of all opinions, every obstacle is an opportunity. If you contemplate enough, all the walls collapse on their own.

—Can there be more than one twin flame?—
—Why am I here?—
"Pluto was a meeting point," they said.

Collaborative creation by Andrés Briceño (@AndBriceno) and Xerografica (@xerografica_) with music by qpRAW (@QPrawNFT).
